%F A002492 a(n) = A081277(3, n-1) = (1+2*n)*binomial(n+1, n-2)*2^2/(n-1) for n > 0. - _Mathias Zechmeister_, Jul 26 2022
%F A002492 E.g.f.: 2*exp(x)*x*(6 + 9*x + 2*x^2)/3. - _Stefano Spezia_, Jul 31 2022
